{"tid":2320524,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"軒達臣留言令利迷重拾足球","createTime":"2020-12-11T01:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T12:31:47.000Z","uid":67225,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"16c70e7d4fd033d9bf21e1f19f39cb01adbfa970","tid":2320524,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:37:45.000Z","msg":"24歲的利物浦球迷Keith Spooner退出了足球比賽兩年，不過紅軍隊長佐敦軒達臣的留言令他重拾足球。<br />\n<br />\nKeith Spooner在紅軍隊長佐敦軒達臣（Jordan Henderson）上載他在利物浦對狼隊時戴上的彩色臂章照片上留言說，「我17歲時出櫃，我經歷了艱難的青少年時期，但讓我感到最舒坦的一件事就是利物浦，看到這張相對我來說意味著全世界，它確實是！」 而紅軍以4:0取勝後，軒達臣對他作出回應說，「You'll never walk alone Keith。如果戴著彩虹臂章對一個人有幫助，那麼它就會取得進展。利物浦歡迎所有人，希望你享受今晚的比賽。」 Keith對軒達臣的回應感到震驚，他說，「一開始我真不敢相信，這真是令人震驚，得到這樣的回應我真不敢相信，聽到利物浦隊長的回音很高興。他對像我這樣的人的影響力是驚人的，事實上他能夠與我聯繫，這確實影響了我想要回到那兒並再次比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">軒就是神</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197ee91737ca01d7b2c3a638ccc0b87a3bf4ad35","tid":2320524,"uid":111460,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkNCJCB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkNCJCB.png&h=a11d935e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53b4789df19bdc453de9da7867d54255bf508dae","tid":2320524,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"新沙維"},{"pid":"f0b2cd1b50077bd84bae2abc0fa9d4ef76d44d1f","tid":2320524,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"197ee91737ca01d7b2c3a638ccc0b87a3bf4ad35","tid":2320524,"uid":111460,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkNCJCB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkNCJCB.png&h=a11d935e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"我唔係紅軍球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f